title: For Sale/Trade:  Glock 30 Gen 3 HIGHLY UPGRADED w/ Lots of Ammo options
postcontent:
Glock 30 Gen 3 .45 ACP. Has Trijicon HD Green Night Sights installed. Titanium striker and block for smooth, rapid cycling, and faster reset, when used in conjunction they work very well in producing a smoother cycle and clean break. Ghost trigger system for a clean 4 lb pull, with a Glock factory smooth surface trigger not found standard on the G30. The standard serrated trigger can cause point of impact drift when the trigger finger drags across the trigger face. Pearce grip extensions for better control while not giving up conceal ability . Titanium alloy assembly pins and take down that are drift, wear, and corrosion resistant. Vickers extended and contoured mag release and Glock extended slide release. All original factory parts, paperwork, hardware, hardcase, Glock Holster and mag pouch, two 10 round magazines are included. This G30 is made in Austria with the dark black Tennifer finish that is proven to last longer then the newer grayish finish. This pistol has extremely light wear and only range use and looks new. The pistol has not had enough rounds fired in it to even break it in. I use this same setup in many other Glocks (21, 22,23,27,) and if works flawlessly and holds up perfectly, much better then out of the box.

Any upgrades can be un done. All factory parts are included.

Pistol fires extremely well. It has a crisp, light and clean break with tight groups. While it is outstanding I use the M&Ps and Rugers more which has left the G30 sitting in the safe.

May include up to 400 round 230 Winchester FMJ and up to 200 Defense rounds depending on trade. Also have additional G30 (10rd) and G21 (13 rd) magazines depending on trade.

title: For Sale/Trade:  1950's Chicom Sino-Soviet SKS. 95% Matching
postcontent:
This item is a rare Sino-Soviet SKS made by China in the 1950's with the aid of Russian materials, labor, and oversight. It has no Arsenal marking and was made before the original /26\ Chinese Arsenal was officiated by the government. *Note that this is a real deal milsurp gun and is not a Norcinco import.*

This gun came packed in cosmoline, which has since been removed and cleaned to working condition. 

The Front Sight Block was canted and the pins were removed and rubber mallet, vice and square used to recenter it. 

There was slight surface rust and pitting below the wood line on the outer receiver which has been removed before it caused any real damage and there is no longer any traces of it.

The gun is 95 percent matching except for the gastube.

Bayonet is in excellent condition.

title: For Trade:  Glock 30 Gen 3 HIGHLY UPGRADED w/ Lots of Ammo options
postcontent:
Glock 30 Gen 3 .45 ACP. Trijicon HD Green Nights Sights installed. Titanium striker and block for smooth, rapid cycling, and faster reset, when used in conjunction they work very well in producing a smoother cycle and clean break. Ghost trigger system for a clean 4 lb pull, with a Glock factory smooth surface trigger not found standard on the G30. The standard serrated trigger can cause point of impact drift when the trigger finger drags across the trigger face. Pearce grip extensions for better control while not giving up conceal ability . Titanium alloy assembly pins and take down that are drift, wear, and corrosion resistant. Vickers extended and contoured mag release and Glock extended slide release. All original factory parts, paperwork, hardware, hardcase, Glock Holster and mag pouch, two 10 round magazines are included. This G30 is made in Austria with the dark black Tennifer finish that is proven to last longer then the newer grayish finish. This pistol has extremely light wear and only range use and looks new. The pistol has not had enough rounds fired in it to even break it in. I use this same setup in many other Glocks (21, 22,23,27,) and if works flawlessly and holds up perfectly, much better then out of the box.

Any upgrades can be un done. All factory parts are included.

Pistol fires extremely well. It has a crisp, light and clean break with tight groups. While it is outstanding I use the M&Ps and Rugers more which has left the G30 sitting in the safe.

May include up to 400 round 230 Winchester FMJ and up to 200 Defense rounds depending on trade. Also have additional G30 (10rd) and G21 (13 rd) magazines depending on trade. 

Email for more photos, questions, prices work ups. Pistol is NOT for sale.
